WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:05.344
High above a quiet pond, seven paper cranes fly together.

2
00:00:05.744 --> 00:00:09.499
Do you see the little red one, right at the front?

3
00:00:09.899 --> 00:00:14.185
Her name is Mika. But she wasn't always the leader.

4
00:00:14.585 --> 00:00:22.086
Mika's very first fold was crooked. Her wings pointed the wrong way, and she wobbled when she flew.

5
00:00:22.486 --> 00:00:25.347
I can't do it, Mika sighed.

6
00:00:25.747 --> 00:00:31.931
Not yet, said Grandmother Crane. Every fold teaches your wings something new.

7
00:00:32.331 --> 00:00:39.300
So Mika practiced. One fold. Then another. Each one a little braver than the last.

8
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:44.900
Her wobbles turned into swoops. Her swoops turned into loops!

9
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:51.455
And the other cranes said: Mika, you fly so well. Will you show us the way?

10
00:00:51.855 --> 00:00:57.233
Now the whole flock flies together, higher than any crane could fly alone.

11
00:00:57.633 --> 00:01:00.519
Your crane is part of the flock now.

12
00:01:00.919 --> 00:01:03.192
What will you fold next?

